    public class RowData
extends ClusData
implements MSortable, java.io.Serializable
    Multiple rows (tuples) of data. One row (DataTuple) is one instance of the data with target and description attributes.

        public RowData sample(int N,
                      ClusRandomNonstatic rnd)
        Create a random sample with replacement of this RowData. Uses the ClusRandom.RANDOM_SAMPLE random generator
        Parameters:
        N - The size of the random subset
        Returns:
        If N > 0: a new RowData containing the random sample of size N If N == 0: a copy of this RowData object (i.e. no sampling)
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if N < 0
